message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe holds great value for those who appreciate its unique features and benefits. Given its quality and the effort put into its creation, I propose a price of $150 for this item. I understand that value perception varies from person to person, so if $150 feels too high, please let me know your preferred price range and we can discuss a mutually agreeable solution. Thank you for considering this opportunity.
